{"tid":2282650,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 超厚玉子燒 配 枝豆忌廉汁鰻魚燉飯 水耕菜沙律","createTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T07:56:42.000Z","uid":33359,"like":97,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"36207f07120e6023c371311acd3a96be832f811e","tid":2282650,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fOB6eSh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfOB6eSh.jpg&h=d8c49560&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AppWB5E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAppWB5E.jpg&h=d9a70901&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XSE0ji1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXSE0ji1.jpg&h=0a644195&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OotMeSp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOotMeSp.jpg&h=81c135c0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8Y03LM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8Y03LM.jpg&h=7dbaae09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日試吓呢個貴少少既餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個忌廉汁好濃好cream<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入係勁強既忌廉汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後慢慢滲返少少枝豆香出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n飯有啲可惜好似係用珍珠米而唔係意大利米<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n口感偏軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果追求正宗risotto既人可能唔太岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鰻魚就普通現成急凍貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n60蚊你都好難要求食到即燒鰻魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n玉子燒生熟度甜度都岩岩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n很好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落個腰椎L3 L4節好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f30239de559f7805b1840b9a3217d93eae0785","tid":2282650,"uid":19682,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0188fdc1e8067fd341a340f46a3a89f93684c480","tid":2282650,"uid":3820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"又觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8ff77f7e2c96c801f26a756f54e6ba8f241198","tid":2282650,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:30.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"0166b4bfb5ed070d3d34a73a4ed37f96ce947585","tid":2282650,"uid":129695,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:39.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820d509406eefaa4b4c314c19840bb50609deae8","tid":2282650,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"69f30239de559f7805b1840b9a3217d93eae0785","tid":2282650,"uid":19682,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:25.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:40.000Z","msg":"你點知的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b05605990fab7ea880912edfca44a0688ae8fe","tid":2282650,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3485fa39a3fe8afc5f5f4058dfbf2645e9b1661","tid":2282650,"uid":26632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi